@JohnnyBoy7267 
I don't know, I've beated both Uncharted 2 and Uncharted 3 around 4 times each (that doesn't count the many times I've replayed individual chapters) and I prefer Uncharted 2's music.
Don't get me wrong, Uncharted 3 some great tracks (e.g. Ambushed, Badlands, Drake's Return, ect) but some from Uncharted 2 are just stellar (e.g. Reunion, Cornered, City's Secret, ect).
